author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-PCCS Group Bhd Says Unit To Dispose Leasehold Industrial Land For Total Consideration Of 8.5 Mln Rgt

organizations.name: brief-pccs group bhd says unit to dispose leasehold industrial land for total consideration of

text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - Pccs Group Bhd:
* UNIT TO DISPOSE LEASEHOLD INDUSTRIAL LAND FOR TOTAL CASH CONSIDERATION OF 8.5 MILLION RGT TO HARTA PACKAGING INDUSTRIES ‍​
* PROPOSED DISPOSAL WILL NOT HAVE ANY MATERIAL EFFECT ON THE EARNINGS OF PGB FOR THE FY ENDING 31 MARCH 2018‍​ Source text : [ bit.ly/2FLjm5g ] Further company coverage:
